ygData.msgSnippet: ... I didn t really notice an increase in resists, cause I get resisted alot anyway, but I did die two times :( The second time was the worst.  There was a ton
ygData.messageBody:
>From: HiFi Review <hifireview@...>
>
>I had a lot of trouble too. Blue things were resisting and EVERYTHING
>seemed to be coming after me. In a group of 5 players I was the sole
>target of interest. Two big ugly deaths after the patch.

I didn't really notice an increase in resists, cause I get resisted alot
anyway, but I did die two times :(
The second time was the worst. There was a ton of people around and like 5
things randomly decided to train on me.
But the thing is that stuff ramdonly trains on me all the time, so for me
it was business as usual.

If stuff is more aggressive to us and resists more, hehe, I'm in for it.
I'll keep an eye out tonite and if I find anything, I'll post it.

Azboklin the enchanter
